metadata.name: Amethyst
metadata.description:
Amethyst is a product of the Retrograde., when Venus enters Libra.
This is a symbol of bringing peace and harmony to peoples lives. 

Coming to the final stages and the end of the retrograde, challenges and immense growth of ones self and abilities has happened.

We are now living in a time that we can find beauty and peace in the smallest of things. 

The future is vibrant and now is your time.

Medium: prisma coloured pencils on black paper size: 2650 × 3748 pixels
